'''Century Golden Resources Group''' is a Chinese privately held [[real estate development]] company.

It is headed by the Chinese billionaire [[Huang Rulun]], and has over 20,000 employees. The company has invested in 20 five-star hotels and 10 shopping malls, with revenues in 2013 of nearly $5 billion.<ref name=Forbes>{{cite web|title=Huang Rulun|url=https://www.forbes.com/profile/huang-rulun/|website=Forbes|accessdate=12 May 2015}}</ref>

